#
# To run the simple relay (not the scapy version) you need some packages:
##
#

Packages
------

python python-dev python-pip tshark tcpdump git make gcc libpcap-dev


Python Stuff
------
pip install pcapy impacket


####

NOTE:	Depending on your network driver / hardware you might need to turn of VLAN offloading and/or unload the 8021q kernel module!!!
	( ethtool -K eth0 rxvlan off &&  ethtool -K eth0 txvlan off )


####


